  <h1 class="coolvetica">Feature Tour</h1>
</div>
<div class="span-18 last section">
  <div class="span-18 last" onclick="void(0)" data-modal_trigger="true" data-modal_id="dashboard_shot" >
    <div class="span-18 last"><div class="span-13"><h2>The Dashboard</h2></div><div class="span-5 last green_text big_font text_center highlight">click to preview</div></div>
    <div class="span-18 last">Your dashboard is where you can quickly enter tasks when you're busy. Later you can come to your dashboard to organize your tasks by adding them to a plan. Your dashboard also show recent comments from collaborators, upcoming due dates, and recently completed tasks.
    </div>
  </div>
