    <div class="section_rule">&nbsp;</div>
 <div class="span-18 last" onclick="void(0)" data-modal_trigger="true" data-modal_id="plan_shot">
   <div class="span-18 last"><div class="span-13"><h2>Plan Task List</h2></div><div class="span-5 last green_text big_font  text_center highlight">click to preview</div></div>
    <div class="span-18 last">
      You'll notice in this screen shot that there is a simple hierarchy: folders contain plans, and plans contain tasks. This view shows the task list for a plan. You can see the folders in the left-side navigation.
    </div>
  </div>
