     <div class="span-18 last">
       You can add a description, a due date, reminders, and labels to a task. If the plan your task belongs to has been shared with other users, you can assign a task to a user as well, (not shown in this screen shot.).
     </div>
  </div>
  <div  class="form_modal" data-modal="true" data-modal_id="task_shot" style="display:none;"><%= image_tag 'task_shot.png' %>
    <div>&nbsp;<br/></div><div class="tour_modal_closer" onclick="void(0)" data-modal_closer="true" data-modal_id="task_shot">close</div></div>
      <div class="section_rule">&nbsp;</div>
